               <p>I am a <rs id="t17821016-24-viclabel133" type="occupation">coachman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17821016-24-victim260 t17821016-24-viclabel133"></join>. I lost my coat last Sunday was sennight, at night, in <placeName id="t17821016-24-crimeloc134">Bishopsgate-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17821016-24-crimeloc134" type="placeName" value="Bishopsgate-street"></interp>
